---
description: Button package docs + checklists must stay consistent (doc/ phases, example app, publishing).
alwaysApply: true
---

## Documentation requirements (always)

- Keep detailed guidance in `doc/` (Phase 1/2/3). `README.md` stays short and links to `doc/`.
- Any new button type, state, or effect must be reflected in:
  - `doc/PHASE_1_SETUP.md` (catalog + capability contract + per-button checklist)
  - `doc/PHASE_2_PACKAGE_AND_EXAMPLES.md` (API + example screen coverage)
  - `doc/PHASE_3_PUBLISHING.md` (pub.dev checklist + pana)

## Publishing requirements

- Before publishing to pub.dev:
  - Remove `publish_to: 'none'` in `pubspec.yaml`
  - Update `version` and `CHANGELOG.md`
  - Ensure `LICENSE` exists
  - `flutter analyze` and `flutter test` are clean
  - `example/` runs

